summary: An ordinance accepting deeds of conveyance from Arthur G. Foster and Sadie Foster, husband and wife, dated January 20, 1928; T.H. Methven, widower, dated January 20, 1928; E. Gerald Carver and Frances M. Carver, his wife, date March 2, 1928 Clara V. Albertson and H.E. Turner executors of the last will and testament of Edward Albertson, deceased, dated February 20, 1928; O.E. Anderson and Elsie, his wife, dated July 13, 1931.
